Tmp-relComp.description: Describes if one structure is bigger or smaller relative to another: Scape is bigger than eye

Tmp-relM.description: Describes measurement of one structure relative to another (in some units): Pronotum twice as long as head

Tmp-absM.description: Describes absolute measurement of a structure in some units: Pronotum length 2mm.

Tmp-tag.description: Inserts id tag for an individual: head:id-78a0f8

(OP alias) bfo-0000051.description: (OP) obo.BFO_0000051: a core relation that holds between a whole and its part

(OP alias) bfo-0000050.description: (OP) obo.BFO_0000050: a core relation that holds between a part and its whole

(OP alias) ro-0000053.description: (OP) obo.RO_0000053: Inverse of characteristic_of; former label: bearer_of

(OP alias) ro-0000052.description: (OP) obo.RO_0000052: a relation between a specifically dependent continuant (the characteristic) and any other entity (the bearer), in which the characteristic depends on the bearer for its existence.

(OP alias) ro-0015007.description: (OP) obo.RO_0015007: q1 increased_in_magnitude_relative_to q2 if and only if magnitude(q1) > magnitude(q2). Here, magnitude(q) is a function that maps a quality to a unit-invariant scale.

(OP alias) ro-0015008.description: (OP) obo.RO_0015008: q1 decreased_in_magnitude_relative_to q2 if and only if magnitude(q1) < magnitude(q2). Here, magnitude(q) is a function that maps a quality to a unit-invariant scale.
